
## 🌐 CAN-to-Ethernet Gateway

A **Raspberry Pi 5** equipped with an **MCP2515 CAN Controller** acts as the communication gateway between the CAN network and the Ethernet network.

The gateway continuously:

- Receives CAN frames from the Receiver ECU
- Decodes incoming telemetry
- Encapsulates the data into UDP packets
- Transmits the packets over Ethernet
- Delivers telemetry to the monitoring PC in real time

